data.description: Golfers Paradise! This Townhome Sits on The Arnold Palmer Course In Windermere PGA National. This SpaciousTwo Bedroom 2.5 Bathroom1 Car Garage has Plenty of Storage & Parking and Steps from the Clubhouse and Pool. Roof, AC, & Waterheater have all been updated. Hardwood Floors & Tile Throughout. Wonderful Patio Area to Enjoy Views, Barbecues and Sunsets. Great location with Access to Excellent Restaurants & Shopping and only 15 min to Palm Beach International Airport. Florida Living At It's Finest!
